#. +> trunk6 stable6
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_d90stairsteppingfix.xml:4
#, kde-format
msgid "Nikon D90 Stairstepping fix"
msgstr "Nikon D90 段差修復"

#. +> trunk6 stable6
#: data/effects/frei0r/frei0r_d90stairsteppingfix.xml:8
#, fuzzy, kde-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Removes stairstepping artifacts from Nikon D90's 720p videos.\n"
#| "        <full><![CDATA[Sharp lines in videos from the Nikon D90 show "
#| "steps each 8th or 9th line, assumedly\n"
#| "        due to poor downsampling. These can be smoothed out with this "
#| "filter if they become too annoying.]]></full>\n"
#| "        "
msgid ""
"Removes stairstepping artifacts from Nikon D90's 720p videos.\n"
"        Sharp lines in videos from the Nikon D90 show steps each 8th or 9th "
"line, assumedly\n"
"        due to poor downsampling. These can be smoothed out with this filter "
"if they become too annoying.\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"Nikon D90 の 720p ビデオで発生する、段差形の出力を解消します。\n"
"        <full><![CDATA[Nikon D90 で撮影したビデオで、8 行または 9 行単位に鋭"
"い線が現われてしまう現象です。おそらくはダウンサンプリング機能が乏しいことに"
"よるものと\n"
"        思われます。これを使用することで、これらの厄介な表示を取り除いてス"
"ムーズな表示にすることができます。]]></full>\n"
"        "

